{
	"description": "the default template generated by npm init origami-component",
	"keywords": ["template"],
	"origamiType": "component",

	"origamiVersion": 1,
	"brands": ["wrong", "internal"],
	"support": "https://github.com/Financial-Times/default-template/issues",
	"supportContact": {
		"email": "chee.rabbits@ft.com",
		"slack": "financialtimes/#origami-chat"
	},
	"supportStatus": "experimental",
	"browserFeatures": {},
	"demosDefaults": {
		"sass": "demos/src/demo.scss",
		"js": "demos/src/demo.js",
		"documentClasses": "",
		"dependencies": []
	},
	"demos": [
		{
			"title": "A Useful Demo",
			"name": "demo",
			"template": "demos/src/demo.mustache",
			"description": "Description of the demo",
			"brands": [7, "internal"]
		},
		{
			"title": "Pa11y",
			"name": "pa11y",
			"template": "demos/src/pa11y.mustache",
			"description": "Accessibility test will be run against this demo",
			"hidden": true
		}
	]
}
